mani Privé</p><p>4，Jennifer Lawrence in Dior</p><p>5，Margot Robbie in Chanel</p><p>6，Gal Gadot in Givenchy gown and Tiffany necklace</p><p>7，Eiza Gonzalez in Ralph Lauren</p><p>8，Zoey Deutch in Elie Saab</p><p>9，Saoirse Ronan in Calvin Klein</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001140i9cDZfkvxKzeW6Rm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.358712\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803060011031Sm5V9AXbKtUq8Rf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001152XyiY63qLCeRTProm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001156gzCUQr043cASoLl5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803060011597AmWUle2EsBGohdn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001204EI8DGYBQmRJ1wbUt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001207awUENjAQsFJnSCtb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001211yclX1KsiaPNjY0dM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306001218USp4VL8hvEIl7y2d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.453880\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Balenciaga</p>"}